{
  "texts": [
    "The inadequacies of the review protocol are revealed and corrected during this pilot study.",
    "Next, the articles are distributed to all authors for revision, and revision of an article by at least two authors is ensured during the review process to eliminate biases.",
    "While investigating the authors assigned articles at least one category in each section of the review protocol.",
    "However, articles can be assigned more than one category whenever possible.",
    "Therefore, the number of total articles mapped in each category shows some variance."
  ]
}